data.description: Welcome to the embodiment of sophistication and comfort at 10403 Fluxus Way, a jewel in the Meridiana masterplan community. This exquisite 4-bedroom home with 3 full baths unfolds over 2,737 sqft of refined living space, designed with meticulous attention to detail. Enter into a welcoming home office accentuated with French doors and a lofty 12-foot ceiling. The generously-sized game room and family room, blessed with abundant natural light from a wall of windows, create an inviting atmosphere. The well-equipped kitchen boasts a pantry and an expansive island, catering to culinary enthusiasts. Your private sanctuary, the primary suite, is a serene retreat with a garden tub, separate glass-enclosed shower, and an oversized walk-in closet. The property's covered patio with outdoor kitchen plumbing and a two-car garage add to the conveniences. Experience the joy of residing in a vibrant, amenity-rich community. Welcome to your Texan dream home!
